== Registration ==

As DESY has a fairly relaxed security policy, the registration procedure is rather simple: just write an email to 
[mailto:eugen.wintersberger@desy.de eugen.wintersberger@desy.de] announcing your attendance. 
The mail should include the following information

* your name
* your institute 
* additional equipment like monitors and/or keyboards if you need one. 

No gate passes are required to enter the site. However, I will prepare some badges for you in case you're getting lost ;).

